      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/p ">There are two optional
relay boards <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A077</b> and <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A078</b> with 16 relays each. The
relay boards are located in the low voltage section. The input signal
at X017 is sent from the controller board.</p>
            <fig platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/fig ">
               <image href="../../Images/Relay-boards_A077-A078_0000363800.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
               <note class="- topic/note "> If additional relays are needed, an additional relay board
can be placed on top of the first one.</note>
            </fig>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
